verbose_text: We do not know for certain what causes the increase of tdTomato positive cells in culture, but a higher demand to establish cell-cell contacts in culture leads to increased Cdh5 (Vascular Endothelial Cadherin, VE-Cadherin) promoter activity, and it seems plausible that this could contribute to higher levels of background Cdh5 (PAC)-CreER T2 activity.
